{"filter":false,"title":"big-data-cloud-mobile.1.php","tooltip":"/technologies/big-data-cloud-mobile.1.php","undoManager":{"mark":82,"position":82,"stack":[[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":67,"column":6},"end":{"row":71,"column":14},"action":"remove","lines":["<p class=\"methodText\">With users rapidly changing the way that they use technology, and Mobile, Social and the Cloud being adopted at a searing pace, it is only logical to say that the value of Big Data for enterprises has just gone into the sky this century. The emergence of Omni-Channel marketing means that the way enterprises engage their customers is changing as well. Users are now more open to engaging in Mobile and Cloud options, and with Security being given added emphasis, the claim for these technologies is becoming stronger everyday.  ","        </p>","        <p class=\"methodText\">If you think its time you re-invented your enterprise, then we can help you do that. With our teams working day-in day-out at our State-of-the-Art <a class=\"linkText\" href=\"../why/innovation.php\"><strong>Innovation Center</strong></a>, we get to play around with the latest technologies. This gives us a chance to understand existing business models and bring innovative ideas to the table to re-invent your business cycle and drive growth. </p>","        <p class=\"methodText\"> Our expertise in the space of integration ensures that we are the best choice for your Mobile (or) Cloud strategy. With our innovative integration techniques and prebuilt components, our teams can help rapidly integrate all of your existing IT investments to Cloud (or) Mobile Applications. ","        </p>  "]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":67,"column":6},"end":{"row":109,"column":10},"action":"insert","lines":["<div class=\"bs-example\">","  <div class=\"panel-group\" id=\"accordion\">  ","  <div class=\"tab-content\">","  <div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"collpaseone\">","          <div class=\"panel panel-default\">","            <div class=\"panel-heading\">","              ","                <h4 class=\"panel-title\">","                    <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" href=\"#collapseOne\">1. What is HTML?</a>","                </h4>","            </div>","            <div id=\"collapseOne\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse \">","                <div class=\"panel-body\">","                    <p>HTML stands for HyperText Markup Language. HTML is the main markup language for describing the structure of Web pages. <a href=\"http://www.tutorialrepublic.com/html-tutorial/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more.</a></p>","                </div>","            </div>","        </div>","        <div class=\"panel panel-default\">","            <div class=\"panel-heading\">","                <h4 class=\"panel-title\">","                    <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" href=\"#collapseTwo\">2. What is Bootstrap?</a>","                </h4>","            </div>","            <div id=\"collapseTwo\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\">","                <div class=\"panel-body\">","                    <p>Bootstrap is a powerful front-end framework for faster and easier web development. It is a collection of CSS and HTML conventions. <a href=\"http://www.tutorialrepublic.com/twitter-bootstrap-tutorial/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more.</a></p>","                </div>","            </div>","        </div>","        <div class=\"panel panel-default\">","            <div class=\"panel-heading\">","                <h4 class=\"panel-title\">","                    <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" href=\"#collapseThree\">3. What is CSS?</a>","                </h4>","            </div>","            <div id=\"collapseThree\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\">","                <div class=\"panel-body\">","                    <p>CSS stands for Cascading Style Sheet. CSS allows you to specify various style properties for a given HTML element such as colors, backgrounds, fonts etc. <a href=\"http://www.tutorialrepublic.com/css-tutorial/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more.</a></p>","                </div>","            </div>","        </div>","    </div>","    </div>"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":109,"column":10},"end":{"row":110,"column":0},"action":"insert","lines":["",""]},{"start":{"row":110,"column":0},"end":{"row":110,"column":4},"action":"insert","lines":["    "]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":110,"column":4},"end":{"row":110,"column":5},"action":"insert","lines":["<"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":110,"column":5},"end":{"row":110,"column":6},"action":"insert","lines":["/"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":110,"column":6},"end":{"row":110,"column":7},"action":"insert","lines":["d"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":110,"column":7},"end":{"row":110,"column":8},"action":"insert","lines":["i"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":110,"column":8},"end":{"row":110,"column":9},"action":"insert","lines":["v"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":110,"column":9},"end":{"row":110,"column":10},"action":"insert","lines":[">"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":110,"column":10},"end":{"row":111,"column":0},"action":"insert","lines":["",""]},{"start":{"row":111,"column":0},"end":{"row":111,"column":4},"action":"insert","lines":["    "]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":217,"column":2},"end":{"row":217,"column":3},"action":"insert","lines":["<"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":217,"column":3},"end":{"row":217,"column":4},"action":"insert","lines":["/"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":217,"column":4},"end":{"row":217,"column":5},"action":"insert","lines":["d"]},{"start":{"row":217,"column":5},"end":{"row":217,"column":6},"action":"insert","lines":["i"]}]}],[{"group":"doc","deltas":[{"start":{"row":217,"column":6},"end":{"row":217,"column":7},"action":"insert","lines":[